777.en_source: This is the letter that Lily hid from Quinn.
777.sl_trans: To je pismo, ki ga je Lily skrivala pred Quinnom.

778.sl_source: Hotela je, da ga najde, ko diplomira.
778.en_source: She wanted her to find it on her graduation day.
778.sl_trans: Želela je, da ga najde na dan diplome.

779.sl_source: Skušala jo je prepričati, da ga prebere prej.
779.en_source: She tried to get her to read it early.
779.sl_trans: Poskušala jo je pripraviti do tega, da bi jo prebrala že prej.

780.en_source: She was trying to reach Quinn.

782.sl_source: –Lily, vem, da si jo hotela doseči.
782.en_source: Lily, I know you were trying to reach her.
782.sl_trans: Lily, vem, da si jo poskušala doseči.

783.sl_source: Vemo, da si hotela, da prebere to pismo.
783.en_source: We know that you wanted her to read this letter.
783.sl_trans: Vemo, da ste želeli, da prebere to pismo.

790.sl_source: Še nekdo drug je danes z nami.
790.en_source: Someone else is here with us.
790.sl_trans: Z nami je še nekdo drug.

791.sl_source: Nekdo, ki res želi govoriti s tabo.
791.en_source: Someone who really wants to talk to you.
791.sl_trans: Nekdo, ki se resnično želi pogovarjati z vami.

793.sl_source: Moram vedeti, da je to resnično.
793.en_source: I need to know that this is real.
793.sl_trans: Vedeti moram, da je to resnično.

795.sl_source: Govori nekaj o odru in o avdiciji.
795.en_source: She's saying something about a stage, an audition.

796.sl_source: Pravi, da si hotela vedeti, ali je bila s tabo, ko si bila na odru.
796.en_source: She says that when you were on stage, you wanted to know if she was there.
796.sl_trans: Pravi, da si na odru želel vedeti, ali je tam tudi ona.

798.en_source: And she was so proud of you.
798.sl_trans: In bila je tako ponosna nate.

799.sl_source: Želi da oba, ti in Sean, vesta, da vama je ni treba več iskati.
799.en_source: She wants you, and you, Sean, to know that you don't need to look for her anymore.
799.sl_trans: Želi, da ti in ti, Sean, veš, da ti je ni treba več iskati.

800.en_source: Because she'll always be with you.

802.sl_source: Vedno vama bo stala ob strani.
802.en_source: She's gonna be standing right beside you.

803.sl_source: Čeprav je ne bosta videla, bo tukaj.
803.en_source: And even though you can't see her, she's there.
803.sl_trans: In čeprav je ne vidite, je tam.

804.sl_source: Kadarkoli bosta zmedena ali osamljena, vama bo šepetala v uho.
804.en_source: And anytime you're feeling confused or alone, she's gonna be whispering in your ear.
804.sl_trans: Kadarkoli se boste počutili zmedeni ali osamljeni, vam bo šepetala na uho.

805.sl_source: Nikoli ne bo prišla nazaj, kajne?
805.en_source: She's never coming back again, is she?
805.sl_trans: Ne bo se nikoli več vrnila, kajne?

811.en_source: Is that the first time you've seen a Ghost?

814.en_source: You never get used to it.
814.sl_trans: Na to se nikoli ne navadiš.

815.sl_source: Spektralna videnja, to mi je pa všeč.
815.sl_trans: Spektralna opažanja, to mi je všeč.

821.sl_source: Očitno je, da potrebujeta eden drugega.
821.en_source: It's clear you both need each other.
821.sl_trans: Jasno je, da oba potrebujeta drug drugega.

822.en_source: Maybe we should go into business together?
822.sl_trans: Morda bi morala skupaj začeti poslovati?

823.sl_source: Niste rekli, da je ta posel preveč nevaren in da lahko umrete.
823.en_source: I thought you said this business was too dangerous for you and you said it could kill you.
823.sl_trans: Mislil sem, da ste rekli, da je ta posel za vas preveč nevaren in da vas lahko ubije.

824.en_source: Well, everybody's gonna die one day.

825.sl_source: Mislim, da je skrajni čas, da se spravim iz hiše, dokler sem še živa.
825.en_source: I think it is high time for me to get out of my house while I'm still alive.
825.sl_trans: Mislim, da je skrajni čas, da se umaknem iz hiše, dokler sem še živ.

828.sl_source: Potem pa me odpeljita do avta.
828.en_source: Well then, take me to my car.

830.sl_source: Mislim tudi, da bi morala obleči kaj boljšega, če bomo delali skupaj.
830.en_source: I also think that you guys should think about wearing something a little better, if we're gonna be working together.
830.sl_trans: Mislim tudi, da bi morali razmisliti o tem, da bi nosili kaj boljšega, če bomo delali skupaj.

831.sl_source: Ta majica je zelo redek kos oblačila.
831.en_source: I'll have you know this tee is extremely rare.
831.sl_trans: Vem, da je ta majica izjemno redka.

835.en_source: What would you have us wear instead?
835.sl_trans: Kaj bi nas namesto tega oblekli?

836.sl_source: Srajco in kravato, to bi bilo v redu.
836.en_source: Shirt and tie might be nice.
836.sl_trans: Srajca in kravata bi bila lahko lepa.

839.en_source: Thank you for looking after me.

840.sl_source: Tudi jaz imam rada tebe, Jack.
840.sl_trans: Tudi jaz te imam rada, Jack.
